research_municipality_step.notes: La Joya, TX operates under a Home-Rule municipal corporation with a Council-Manager form of government, governed by a Mayor and four Councilmembers elected at-large. There was a minor discrepancy in the Mayor Pro-Tem role between different pages of the city's website; the City Council page lists Enrique Cantu as Mayor Pro-Tem, while the 'Our Team' page lists Angie Garza. The City Council page provides a more detailed breakdown of roles and places, which was prioritized.
